@startuml
start
:User enters symptom, duration, severity, and context;
:System checks deterministic safety rules;
if (Emergency-like trigger found?) then (yes)
  :Show safety notice;
  :Recommend urgent professional medical help;
  stop
else (no)
  :Generate follow-up questions;
  :User answers follow-up questions;
  :Generate structured symptom summary;
  :Assign non-diagnostic triage guidance;
  :Display summary with persistent disclaimer;
endif
stop
@enduml
